        * ace/OS_NS_wchar.h:

          #included ace/os_include/os_errno.h. Needed for builds where
          ACE_HAS_SIGNAL_SAFE_OS_CALLS is defined. Thanks to Kobi
          Cohen-Arazi for the patch.

