        * ace/Object_Manager.cpp:
          CBuilderX Preview defines _MSC_VER and __BORLANDC__ so only use
          _CrtSetReportMode when _MSC_VER is defined and not __BORLANDC__.
          Borland isn't making thing easier to maintain.

